snippet.title: Bubble Bobble Lost Cave v1.2 - Mame 0.167 -
snippet.description:
Here it is! Bubble Bobble Lost Cave was a new addition on Mame 0.167 too. In this game all levels for the classic 1986 game were changed for others that are available on home console ports (NES, Master System and Game Boy as example).

Now music repeats in my head again and again lol

- DOWNLOAD - (Rom is not included)

32 bits - http://adf.ly/1QnJ5i
64 bits - http://adf.ly/1QnP7f
